config BR2_PACKAGE_EMBRA_DESKTOP
	bool "embra-desktop"
	help
	  embraOS iced GUI client. Connects to embra-apid over gRPC and
	  renders the operator UI as a Wayland client of embra-comp's
	  fullscreen kiosk surface. Replaces embra-console in graphical
	  boots. The binary is cross-compiled against Buildroot's
	  staging tree (iced 0.14 pulls libwayland-client / xkbcommon /
	  softbuffer via FFI; the standalone musl.cc toolchain doesn't
	  ship those libs). Installed via the rootfs overlay in
	  scripts/build-image.sh Step 4.5.
